Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.59,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}遊魔ヶ時へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}甘ったるい安寧は夢の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.14,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仮面越しの愛も偽物に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.23,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}この難解な世界　難解な世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:05.48,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心融け会えばいずれ暴かれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.02,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}アイムノットルーニー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}別々に刻んだ秒針の行く先は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑ってるの日々？泣いてるの日々？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:15.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}隠し合った傷跡を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.70,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ハイドアンドシークで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.99,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さあさ探して頂戴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.46,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}邪魔しないで頂戴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被命運攪弄  多舛的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.57,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無邊的孤獨中  只有單行的秒針
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:30.07,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}滴  答  滴  答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:32.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}刻下一道道因果與憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.70,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}令人不適的奢侈的道德困境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.20,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}屏住呼吸  在空虛旅途的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.83,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}滴  答  滴  答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}歡迎回到天堂與地獄的庭園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}白晝  夜晚  明天  後天  來回交替
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.96,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使現在並無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:51.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}眯起看向現實的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.59,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}游魔之時已到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}甜蜜的安寧似同夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.14,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}面具下的愛也化作虛偽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}面對這難解的世界  難解的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:05.48,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只要我們心靈合一  或許就能找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我並不是瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}各自行走的秒針所要抵達的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是充滿笑聲還是淚水的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:15.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}互相遮掩住的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.70,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就請你用捉迷藏的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.99,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}來找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.46,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不要妨礙我們
Comment: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:46.04,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From the day we promised
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:49.00,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}漕ぎ始めた小さなボート
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:52.38,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Until we get to the place we dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.59,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向かず along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.21,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}To go straight 息を揃え
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.97,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは同じ歌を歌う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.64,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}赤なら止まれ no rush
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:05.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Cuz it’s a long long way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:09.06,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if the heavy rain is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We really don’t care
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:14.15,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾いた風も追い風に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:16.40,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いっそ遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:18.23,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The gate is open
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.86,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遠ざかる skyline
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:22.49,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}動き出した life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:26.33,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The sunrise 登るまで seize the night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.54,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I keep dreaming of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:33.29,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Moonlit 僕らの描いた story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:36.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Prove it その日までの journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:40.76,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How many miles can we go forward tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:02.45,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\bord1}How many miles can we go forward tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:46.04,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們立下誓言的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:49.00,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的木船駛向旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:52.38,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向著我們夢中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.59,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無需留念  一心向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.21,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}邁著相同的步子前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.97,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們異口同聲地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.64,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}紅燈就歇歇  不必著急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:05.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們要走的路還很長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:09.06,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使暴風雨將要到來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.89,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們也不會在意分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:14.15,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不如就乘上乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:16.40,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}飛向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:18.23,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}門已經敞開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.86,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無垠的天際線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:22.49,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生命開始轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:26.33,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}抓住夜晚  跟隨日出的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.54,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在夢中呼喚黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:33.29,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}月光灑下我們描繪的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:36.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}證明我們漫漫旅途的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:40.76,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今夜的我們  還能前進幾里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:02.45,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\bord1}今夜的我們  還能前進幾里？
